headline: Biden Tells These Two GOP Senate Candidates To Quit Presidential Council Or Be Fired
author: IWB
sentences: In a post on Wednesday, Oz, who is a candidate in Pennsylvania, said the administration sent him a letter requesting he resign from the President’s Council on Sports, Fitness & Nutrition.
Lexi Lonas from The Hill reports, President Biden has asked Republican Senate candidates Herschel Walker and Mehmet Oz to quit their positions on a presidential council or be removed.
